            <div class="course-content">
                <h2>Fullstack Development: Build End-to-End Web Applications</h2>
                <p>Fullstack development combines both frontend and backend skills to create complete web applications from start to finish. This comprehensive course will equip you with the knowledge and hands-on experience to become a versatile fullstack developer.</p>

                <h3>Course Overview</h3>
                <p>This intensive 16-week program covers the entire web development stack. You'll learn to build complete, production-ready applications by mastering both client-side and server-side technologies.</p>

                <h3>What You'll Learn</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Frontend development (HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, React)</li>
                    <li>Backend development (Node.js, Express)</li>
                    <li>Database design and management (MongoDB, MySQL)</li>
                    <li>RESTful API development</li>
                    <li>Authentication and authorization systems</li>
                    <li>Full application deployment workflows</li>
                    <li>Testing and debugging across the stack</li>
                    <li>Performance optimization techniques</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Course Structure</h3>
                <p>The course follows a comprehensive approach to fullstack development:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Frontend Fundamentals:</strong> HTML, CSS, and JavaScript essentials</li>
                    <li><strong>Advanced Frontend:</strong> React and modern JavaScript frameworks</li>
                    <li><strong>Backend Basics:</strong> Server-side programming with Node.js</li>
                    <li><strong>Database Integration:</strong> Working with SQL and NoSQL databases</li>
                    <li><strong>API Development:</strong> Building and consuming RESTful services</li>
                    <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> Implementing secure user management</li>
                    <li><strong>Deployment:</strong> Cloud hosting and DevOps basics</li>
                    <li><strong>Capstone Project:</strong> Building a complete fullstack application</li>
                </ol>

                <h3>Prerequisites</h3>
                <p>Basic programming knowledge is recommended but not required. This course is designed to accommodate beginners while challenging those with prior experience.</p>

               
